Patch Set 1:

If lnet_cpt_of_md_page() (maybe just lnet_cpt_of_md(), or lnet_cpt_of_md_bulk()?) returns lnet_cpt_current() for the unknown case, then the start of lnet_select_pathway() could look like this:

    if (msg->msg_md)
        md_cpt = lnet_cpt_of_md(msg->msg_md->md_bulk_handle);
    else
        md_cpt = lnet_cpt_current();
    cpt = md_cpt;
    lnet_net_lock(cpt);
again:

You may or may not consider that to be an improvement.
